&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;


&lt;h3&gt;Conclusion&lt;/h3&gt;
It was my first Droidcon UK and I will definitely get a ticket for the 2015 event as soon as possible.
Top venue, top speakers and a top organisation. Well done, Droidcon UK. See you next year.
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;


